title: Is there a picture of Michigan Goff? Whitmer without a mask?
subtitle: Whitmer has a gold-colored jacket that she wears repeatedly, a fact that has been used to spread misleading information.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A picture showing Gove Michigan. Gretchen Whitmore doesn't wear a mask at a press conference where she announces the new restrictions imposed on Coved 19.
